e. However, further investigations including genetic analyses of nuclear genes are needed to test the latter hypothesis.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Tu, Vuong Tan", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Hassanin, Alexandre", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "G\u00f6rf\u00f6l, Tam\u00e1s", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Arai, Satoru", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Fukui, Dai", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Thanh, Hoang Trung", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Son, Nguyen Truong", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Furey, Neil M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Csorba, G\u00e1bor", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/5f2aac6c2156422de12893bf92b5d320", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/3cc2d84b3162458e94720ed463d3dd0bc154147fadda78624376cbc09c3f58e3", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/YXLNGC7G", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/YXLNGC7G", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/13cc06ef29ce689bc6c63e85cffe864f!/b251736-254179", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "3", "pages": "177-198", "title": "Journal of Zoological Systematics and Evolutionary Research", "volume": "55"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/5f2